reviewText: Item is as advertised; love it!

I gave it 4 stars. Not as light and comedic as Strictly Ballroom but still very touching and romantic albeit a bit dark.

Hilarious though how they have thugs in ballroom dancing breaking legs. LOL

A must see k-drama.  It is very beautiful and touching.  Anyone who is an artist will have an added appreciation to his/her art.  It's really how one should do something...with passion, with your heart!
